---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="About me | Lucy Epoxy Studio" description="The story behind Lucy Epoxy Studio." lang="en" pathname="/en/about-me">
  <Header ctaHref="/en/contact" ctaLabel="Get a quote" />
  <main class="section-sm"><div class="container" style="display:grid;gap:1rem;">
    <img src="/images/about-workshop.jpg" alt="Lucyna at work" class="card" style="width:100%;max-height:520px;object-fit:cover;" />
    <article class="card" style="padding:1.3rem;white-space:pre-line;line-height:1.7;">
As a person with a disability, I searched for my place for a long time — not only in the job market, but also in life. Many paths were closed to me, and that is exactly when I discovered craftsmanship, which became my chance, my strength, and a new beginning.

What started as an idea for my own business gradually turned into a true passion. In my work I found myself, meaning, and the joy of creating. I complete every order with heart, care, and gratitude, because I know how much it means to do what you love.

By choosing my services, you support not only a small business, but also a story of determination, courage, and faith that dreams can come true despite obstacles. I create with passion and for people.

<br><br>
I invite you to collaborate<br>
<span class="signature">Lucyna</span>
    </article>
  </div></main>
  <Footer />
  <style>
    .signature {
      font-family: 'Segoe Script', 'Brush Script MT', cursive;
      color: #1e3a5f;
      font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.8vw, 1.7rem);
      display: inline-block;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>